lScope\">381b12</biblScope> </bibl> ; of milk, etc., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be concocted</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg012:776a:26\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ GA\">GA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">776a26</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg012:777a:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">777a7</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n82707.5\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἶνος π. τὰ σῖτα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">promotes the digestion of</tr_> food, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:26a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.26a</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n82707.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph., of diseases, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πέσσεται νοῦσος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">is 'concocted', comes to a crisis</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg004.perseus-grc1:42\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Acut.\">Acut.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">42</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n82707.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph., also, mostly in bad sense, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χόλον πέσσειν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">nurse, brood over</tr_> one's wrath, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλ᾽ ἐπὶ νηυσὶ χόλον θυμαλγέα</foreign> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πέσσει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0